<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/nhs-blood-and-transplant> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "NHS Blood and Transplant (NHSBT) is responsible for the supply of blood, organs, tissues and stem cells. It collects and supplies blood to hospitals in England and is the organ donation organisation for the UK. NHSBT is a special health authority, sponsored by the Department of Health and Social Care ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
